# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:28
translate chinese maris4_1f958b5b:

    # fr "That's cool. I love it when people are passionate about things, even if it's something I'm not really into."
    fr "挺好的。我喜欢看到人们对某件事充满热情，哪怕那不是我感兴趣的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:32
translate chinese maris4_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_ohcool1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:33
translate chinese maris4_7b389c9e:

    # fr "That's cool. I don't expect us to both like the exact same things, you know?"
    fr "挺好的。我本来就不指望我们俩喜欢完全一样的东西，你知道吗？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:34
translate chinese maris4_b1a6e571:

    # fr "What would be the fun in that?"
    fr "那样有什么意思呢？"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:35
translate chinese maris4_f6fc400b:

    # fr "You introduce me to some new stuff and I'll introduce you to some new stuff too."
    fr "你带我认识一些新事物，我也带你认识一些新事物。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:36
translate chinese maris4_b35da6a1:

    # fr "Then we both become better people."
    fr "这样我们都会变得更好。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:37
translate chinese maris4_83f8048e:

    # pc "I like that."
    pc "我喜欢这种想法。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:40
translate chinese maris4_dc3a3c2b:

    # fr "I hope you're not just saying that because I don't like sports."
    fr "希望你不是因为我不喜欢运动才这么说的。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:42
translate chinese maris4_7ac8df64:

    # fr "I wouldn't say they're lame, but they're not for me."
    fr "我不会说运动很无聊，但那不是我的菜。"

# game/Scenes/Mari/MariConversations/maris4.rpy:43
translate chinese maris4_11334516:

    # fr "They make a lot of people happy though, so who am I to put them down?"
    fr "不过运动能让很多人开心，我有什么资格去贬低它们呢？"

